{
  "stem": "19795.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't feel like-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't want to say anything because I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't remember the [? true ?] things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When the Russians left, and the Germans came in--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans came in, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a war, so they left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1941, I think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, in '41.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] In '41, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the Germans came, and they took right away my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They take him away because-- yeah, everybody was home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was standing in the window.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some Ukrainian came over-- Ukrainian police-- came over and through the window they made to him like this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he went over to the bed, and he took the [INAUDIBLE] with the Star of David and the jacket, and they took him away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was the 13 of August.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was 3:30 in the afternoon in 1941.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know probably to the Gestapo, or they killed him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's not only him they took.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took a few people there that died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to take always.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was from the first one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, Ukrainian police came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the Ukrainians were working for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't feel anything, but when they came in, so then we don't-- if we didn't see them, then we went to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure, the Ukrainian worked together with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who did it, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they are both-- it was the Ukrainian helped the Germans, and they worked together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is no difference who.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The most important, they took away, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Polish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Polish people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also who was able worked for them, sure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
